---
title: The Big Chicken Salad Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Our chef-curated “perfect plates” are the answer to your dinner woes! Set out a wholesome spread of seared chicken cutlets and salad fixins: fresh mixed greens, carrots, tomato, a shower of crunchy panko breadcrumbs, and a sprinkle of nutty Parmesan cheese. Add toasty garlic bread on the side and serve it all family style so everyone can build their own perfect salad bowl! Order extra tortillas to make wraps and/or bacon for a smoky topper!
